### 1. Basic Search with only query and language (English)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/calories/search-food?query=apple&lang=EN&categoriaId=1 
###

### 2. Basic Search with only query and language (Spanish)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/calories/search-food?query=manzana&lang=ES

###

### 3. Search with category filter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/calories/search-food?query=apple&lang=EN&categoriaId=1

###

### 4. Invalid Search (Query too short - should return 400 Bad Request or 500)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/calories/search-food?query=a&lang=EN

###

### 5. Missing required params (Should return 400 ZodError)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/calories/search-food?query=apple
